          releaseDate: "October 2024",
          genres: ["New Release", "PC"],
          desc: "Published by Miracle Games, Ghost Shooting puts you in the role of a night phantom sniper, controlling the battlefield and delivering precise justice! Take on thrilling bounty missions, experience realistic sniping mechanics, and enjoy stunning slow-motion effects that immerse you in every shot. With diverse battlegrounds, a professional-grade weapon system, and high tactical freedom, find the perfect balance between stealth and attack. Show off your sniper skills and become the ultimate ghost assassin!\n\nBeneath the city's dazzling surface, crime syndicates secretly plot and execute their schemes. As an elite sniper, you must lurk in the shadows, track your targets, and eliminate them with surgical precision. Use terrain for cover, adjust your angle, and exercise patience to wait for the perfect moment to strike. Each flawless kill brings you closer to dismantling the underworld, restoring justice to the city!\n\nYour weapon is your greatest ally! Ghost Shooting offers a vast arsenal, from high-precision sniper rifles to tactical support gear. Unlock and upgrade your firearms to enhance stability and firepower, customizing your unique combat style. Take on global sniper missions, unlock new city maps, and adapt to strategic challenges across diverse environments. Pick up your rifle, fulfill your duty, and protect the world like a silent ghost!\n\nGame Features\nTake on Bounty Missions and Strike with Precision\n\u2022 Ghost Shooting offers hundreds of thrilling missions, from eliminating gang members and assassinating crime bosses to intercepting black-market deals. Every shot counts! Lurk in the shadows, take out targets with precision, and ensure silent execution. Only by calculating bullet trajectories and choosing the perfect sniping angle can you eradicate evil forces and restore justice to the city!\n\nBuild Your Arsenal and Upgrade Deadly Weapons\n\u2022 As an elite sniper, a powerful weapon is key to success! The game features an extensive armory with a wide variety of firearms. Unlock and upgrade weapons, optimize attachments for better stability and firepower, and select the best gear for each mission. With the right tools, every shot becomes lethal, and high-difficulty missions feel effortless!\n \nDrone Assistance for Tactical Advantage\n\u2022 No more going solo on tough missions! Ghost Shooting provides an advanced drone system to scout from a distance, mark enemies, and refine your strategy. Use drones to navigate complex terrain, detect hidden threats, and enhance your precision. Combine strategy with technology to make every kill a flawless execution!\n \nImmersive HD Graphics and Realistic Sound Effects\n\u2022 Ghost Shooting utilizes cutting-edge 3D rendering to create lifelike cityscapes and highly detailed character models. From rooftop hideouts to abandoned factories and shadowy streets, every environment is meticulously designed to feel real. Paired with professional-grade gun sounds, environmental effects, and intense background music, each shot and bullet impact is a breathtaking experience, pulling you deep into the action!\n\nCross-Platform Play for Seamless Sniping\n\u2022 Ghost Shooting supports cross-platform play, allowing you to enjoy high-definition sniping on PC while seamlessly continuing missions on Android. Whether using precise mouse-aiming or quick mobile controls, your progress syncs across devices. Switch effortlessly and dive into action anytime, anywhere!",
