          rating: 4.0,
          isFree: true,
          publisher: "NetEase Games",
          releaseDate: "March 2025",
          genres: ["Fighting", "Multiplayer"],
          desc: "Co-published by Miracle Games, Blazing Beacons: Three Kingdoms brings an epic strategy war experience! Step into the turbulent Three Kingdoms era as a city lord, commanding legendary heroes and scheming for dominance. Featuring a massive map and real-time interactive battles, the game accurately depicts terrain, fortresses, and warfare. Strategize on the fly, adapt to shifting battle conditions, and experience an immersive \"what you see is what you get\" war simulation. With a fast-paced short-season system, new seasons start every month, eliminating prolonged resource drain and delivering pure strategic warfare!\n\nRooted in historical authenticity, the game recreates legendary battles from the Battle of Guandu to the Battle of Yiling, allowing players to relive the grand conflicts of the era. Seamlessly switch battlefield coordinates, monitor friendly and enemy troop movements in real time, and achieve ultimate victory through informed decision-making. Over 300 iconic generals and strategists, including Guan Yu, Zhang Fei, and Zhuge Liang, await your command, ready to help you conquer the land.\n\nEnhance your strategy with renowned scholars and classic military texts, deepening your tactical expertise. Whether engaging in ambush tactics, city sieges, or large-scale legion warfare, showcase your strategic prowess and revel in thrilling battles. The short-season format revolutionizes traditional SLG gameplay with monthly resets, ensuring rapid engagements and new challenges. Even after setbacks, rally your forces, return stronger, and rewrite history in the next season of Three Kingdoms warfare!\n\nSupported Languages: English, Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese.\n\nGame Features\nHeroes Assemble, Legends Return\n\u2022 The game features a full roster of Three Kingdoms-era generals, covering Wei, Shu, Wu, and various warlords, with over 300 legendary figures joining the battlefield. Each general is meticulously crafted based on historical records or classic tales, bringing their unique skills to life. From mighty warriors who crush enemies to brilliant strategists who orchestrate victories, players can freely assemble their ideal lineup, unleashing tactical brilliance and rewriting history.\n\nGrand Battlefields, Strategy Reigns\n\u2022 A vast sandbox map removes traditional constraints, allowing players across the server to engage in large-scale strategic warfare. Infantry, archers, cavalry, and siege weapons each play a crucial role, supporting diverse combat scenarios including skirmishes, sieges, and national wars. Master the terrain, anticipate enemy movements, and deploy troops with precision\u2014only those with superior tactics and flexible strategies can claim supremacy over the land!\n \nMassive Kingdom Wars, Flames of Conquest\n\u2022 With thousands of players clashing in real-time, the game delivers a truly immersive Three Kingdoms war experience. Factions rise, armies march, and battles erupt across the land in a relentless struggle for dominance. As the battlefield shifts, commanders must adapt, issuing calculated orders\u2014whether to launch a sudden ambush or fortify strongholds. Outsmart opponents, claim victory, and ascend as the ultimate ruler of the Three Kingdoms!\n \nElite Warriors, Tactical Supremacy\n\u2022 The greatest heroes of the era gather under your banner, awaiting your command! The game features a Strategist System, where brilliant minds shape the battlefield with masterful tactics. Utilize classic military texts and war doctrines to refine your strategic approach. Combat isn't just about stats\u2014it's a battle of wits, where adaptability and precise lineup combinations decide the victor. Analyze enemy formations, counter their strengths, and prove your dominance in this era of war!\n\n Cross-Platform Play, Total Control\n\u2022 Experience seamless cross-platform gameplay between PC and Android, ensuring full command over your empire anytime, anywhere. The PC version provides an immersive large-screen view, enabling strategic planning with a bird's-eye perspective. Meanwhile, the Android version allows for quick tactical adjustments, troop deployment, and real-time battle responses on the go. No matter where you are, stay ahead of the war and seize every opportunity for victory!",
          minReq: {"OS": "Windows 10 64-bit", "CPU": "Intel Core i5-6600K", "RAM": "8 GB", "GPU": "NVIDIA GTX 970", "Storage": "60 GB HDD", "DirectX": "Version 11"},
          recReq: {"OS": "Windows 11 64-bit", "CPU": "Intel Core i7-8700", "RAM": "16 GB", "GPU": "NVIDIA RTX 3060 Ti", "Storage": "60 GB SSD", "DirectX": "Version 12"},
          reviews: [{user:"NightOwl_Plays",avatar:"N",rating:4,date:"Feb 2025",text:"Really solid experience overall. The graphics are stunning and gameplay is smooth. Minor performance hiccups at launch but patches fixed most issues."},{user:"IndieGameFan",avatar:"I",rating:5,date:"Mar 2025",text:"Didn't expect much but this completely blew me away. Hidden gem of the year! Tell all your friends about this one."},{user:"GalacticGamer_99",avatar:"G",rating:5,date:"Mar 2025",text:"Absolutely mind-blowing game! Spent 80+ hours and still discovering new content. One of the best purchases I've ever made on any platform."},{user:"TechGamer_2026",avatar:"T",rating:4,date:"Apr 2025",text:"Great optimization on PC. Runs buttery smooth on mid-range hardware. Developer support has been excellent post-launch."},{user:"FamilyGameNight",avatar:"F",rating:5,date:"Mar 2025",text:"Perfect for playing with kids! Safe, fun and educational. My whole family enjoys it every weekend together."}]
