          desc: "Get ready to hop into a world of festive fun with Easter Bunny EggVenture, the egg\u2011citing spot the difference challenge bursting with springtime charm! Each level presents two cheerful Easter scenes filled with bunnies, baskets, and brightly patterned eggs that seem identical at first glance\u2026 but look again. Hidden among the pastel colors and playful details are clever differences waiting to be discovered. From swapped egg patterns, missing egg baskets, and bunny ears pointing the wrong way, every level puts your observation skills to the test. Race the clock in Challenge Mode for fast paced fun, or take your time in Casual Mode and enjoy the warm, whimsical artwork at your own pace. With simple pick up and\u2011play controls, delightful seasonal illustrations, and that irresistible \u201cjust one more!\u201d feeling, Easter Bunny EggVenture is the perfect game for players who love sharp eyes, charming surprises, and a basketful of visual puzzles.\n\nPublished by\nJolly Lobster Interactive\nDeveloped by\nJolly Lobster Interactive\nRelease date\n3/4/2026",
