          desc: "Your friends are scattered across the city, and the rail network is in pieces! Draw colored tracks, reconnect the railroads, and guide trains back to their stations to find your lost buddies and bring everyone home.\n\nWith each rescue, your hometown slowly recovers, but the puzzles get trickier. Tunnels, crossroads, and clever obstacles will test your logic and creativity as you invent new routes, solve mind-bending challenges, and restore order to the railways.\n\nFeatures:\n- 1000+ handcrafted logic puzzles!\n- 120 extra-large levels full of challenges!\n- Tricky mechanics like gates, crossroads, and obstacles.\n- Multiple solutions that reward creative thinking!\n- Optional hints to help you through tougher levels.\n- A beautiful city full of life waiting to be restored!\n\nChoo Choo! Next station is never-ending fun!\n\nPublished by\nQubicGames S.A.\nDeveloped by\nQubicGames\nRelease date\n11/4/2026",
