          rating: 4.0,
          isFree: false,
          publisher: "Voodoo",
          releaseDate: "November 2019",
          genres: ["Card", "Board", "Casual"],
          desc: "Unroll Ball: A Classic Puzzle with a Modern Twist \ud83c\udfaf\n\nGet ready to put your brain to the test with Unroll Ball, a simple yet addictive tile puzzle game with a contemporary twist. Designed for casual gamers of all ages, this game combines classic gameplay with modern challenges to keep you hooked.\n\nHow to Play\n\n    Slide the tiles to create a seamless path for the ball.\n    Guide the ball to the red goal block while overcoming barriers and brainstorming new solutions.\n    Each level offers a unique challenge, encouraging creative problem-solving and strategic thinking.\n\nWhy You\u2019ll Love Unroll Ball\n\n\u2714\ufe0f Engaging Gameplay: Easy to learn but hard to master, this game keeps you coming back for more.\n\u2714\ufe0f Boost Your Brain: Enhance your visual memory, intelligence, and mental speed while solving fun puzzles.\n\u2714\ufe0f Plenty of Puzzles: Enjoy a variety of challenging levels to keep your mind sharp and entertained.\n\u2714\ufe0f Relax and Focus: Designed to train your problem-solving skills in a calm and enjoyable environment.\n\u2714\ufe0f Brain-Boosting Fun: Improve your critical thinking and decision-making with each level.\n\n\ud83d\udc4d Key Features\n\n    Classic & Star Modes: Choose between timeless gameplay or a more challenging experience.\n    Hints Features: Use hints to guide you when you\u2019re stuck.\n    No Stress, Just Fun: No time limits or pressure\u2014play at your own pace.\n    Pure Gameplay: No ads, no data collection, no internet required\u2014just uninterrupted fun.\n    PC & Xbox Support: Enjoy smooth gameplay on your favorite platforms with intuitive controls.\n\nStart Your Puzzle Journey Today\n\nWhether you\u2019re looking for a relaxing brain exercise or a challenging puzzle experience, Unroll Ball is the perfect choice. Start rolling and solve your way to victory!",
