          publisher: "Crazy Labs",
          releaseDate: "May 2023",
          genres: ["Family", "Kids", "Casual"],
          desc: "Co-Published by Miracle Games, Cooking Playtime: Tasty Street is the most addicting simulation and cooking games experience available. You will prepare, offer unique foreign cuisine\ud83c\udf57\ud83c\udf55\ud83d\ude0b, and have fun with the fast-paced action in the food fever.\n\nLet\u2019s become frenzied chefs, masters of the culinary arts. You may prepare delectable dishes\ud83e\udd58\ud83c\udf5d , travel across several significant places \u2708, embark on diverse food culture trips, and establish your own trendy kitchen empire. In this free and entertaining journey, you may now spread the culinary fever all over the world.\n\nIn your cooking diary \ud83e\udd50and culinary story, you serve a variety of famous dishes such as Sushi, Dimsum, \u2026 as well as making tea, preparing ice cream, many Asian foods, burgers, seafood, baking cupcakes, making coffee, and a variety of fast food... and discovering countless hidden recipes in your excellent restaurants.\n\nYou may play whenever and anywhere you choose \ud83c\udfae\ud83c\udfae\ud83c\udfae- No internet connection is needed after the initial setup. Let's play this free cookery game at our leisure. Take the excitement of culinary matches with you everywhere you go. The journey is Fantastic.\n\nOutstanding feature:\n\ud83c\udf54 Serve hundreds of one-of-a-kind culinary dishes from throughout the world. In this beautiful tour, you will see all of the major streets. \ud83c\udf5f\n\ud83c\udf54 Get a true sense of cooking in the insane kitchen - the finest restaurant ever. You can do anything in your culinary experience: boil, fry, steam, grill... and even if you don't, you'll acquire heaps of cooking skills and new tasty recipes you've never tried before.\n\ud83c\udf54 Improve ingredients to introduce more innovative cuisines to crazed eaters.\n\ud83c\udf54 Keep up with rush hour by correctly managing your time and updating your kitchen appliances.\n\ud83c\udf54 Cook up lucrative combinations, collect large bonuses, and you'll be the winner after completing all of the hard tasks in this cooking craziness voyage.\n\nYou are without a doubt the top of the best at your luxury restaurant!\n\nHOW TO PLAY?\n\ud83c\udf73Collect enough keys to unlock more eateries.\n\ud83c\udf73 Prepare and serve over 300 delicious dinners with fun and joy\n\ud83c\udf73 Improve your ingredients and kitchen equipment.\n\ud83c\udf73 Increase your revenue by providing more consumers in less time.\n\ud83c\udf73 Create a variety of combinations to earn more money and tips from clients.\n\ud83c\udf73 In this choking game, use item packs to increase your cooking strength and choked speed.\n\ud83c\udf73 Make an effort not to squander or overcook any food.\n\nSOME SUGGESTIONS FOR YOU\n\ud83c\udf72Completing unique culinary goals with Magical Boost then instantly well-cooked\n\ud83c\udf72Special pans assist you in ensuring that your food is never overdone.\n\ud83c\udf72Customers are offered meals promptly using Cook Helper\n\ud83c\udf72Use Double Coin to boost your profits. Oh, chef, you're going to be rich.\nNow, do everything you can and give it a try in this chophouse. Get the restaurants back to business.\n\nCulinary heaven awaits you. Let's play this fun, colorful, and magnificent chef kitchen game, for girls, boys, kids, adults, and all fans of fast-cooking games. Diners are famished and queueing outside your well-known eatery.\nChef, a lot of luck today!\n\nDownload Tasty Street for free right now \ud83d\udc49\ud83d\udc49\ud83d\udc49\n _____________________________________________________________________\n\nFollow the official Miracle Games channels for more info.\nOur E-mail: Support@mguwp.com\nOur X: https://x.com/mguwp  \nOur Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MiracleGamesAppStore\nOur Discord: https://discord.gg/tVFXZwp\nMG Global Customer Help & Support Center: https://support.mguwp.com/",
